    "description": "Double your main protein. Whip up your own home-style Korean bibimbap with crispy lean pork mince, spicy gochujang ketchup and sesame-coated spinach rice. Top it with a fried egg to finish and dig in. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
